name: Żeluś Sneak peak
description: Żeluś is a  platforming game built using Construct 2. Move left, right and jump to get through each level. Due to Construct 2 free limitations, I can't develop it longer in this program. That's why I'm going to make a bigger Żeluś on another engine. Only the Polish version is available but you don't have to read to pass this game.
